word_mean_info__list.difference: 多指突然发生的出乎意料的紧急情况或事故。
含义广泛，可指国家存亡、历史、经刘或人的生命、疾病等面临危急关头。也可指好的或恶化的转折点。

list.abstract: emergency，英语单词，可作名词、形容词，翻译为紧急情况、非常时刻、紧急的。

yingyinNormal.en: What the hell? Emergency preparedness drill.
yingyinNormal.zh: 搞毛呀？紧急情况预防演习。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, that's ridiculous! A bathroom emergency is self-explanatory.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这太荒唐了！洗手间紧急情况不言自明。

yingyinNormal.en: Emergency, emergency. Tortoise's up a tree. I don't know why you like climbing tree so much?
yingyinNormal.zh: 紧急情况，紧急情况乌龟爬到树上去了！我不知道为什么你这么喜欢爬树？

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, I'm afraid not. Section seven here, on the right to enter the bathroom in emergency situations, is not specific as to what constitutes an emergency.
yingyinNormal.zh: 恐怕是的，第七部分这里，紧急情况下进入洗手间的权利，没有明确约定什么是紧急情况。

yingyinNormal.en: Maybe we should land now. Emergency. Emergency. Calling rescue helicopter. I'm on my way. You're in luck. We've got a job to do.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们差不多该降落了吧。紧急情况！紧急情况！紧急呼叫救援直升机！好，马上就到，你们真幸运，我们要去执行任务了！

yingyinNormal.en: Why do you guys have so many keys in there anyway? For an emergency just like this.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你怎么会有那么多钥匙？紧急情况，就像现在这样。

yingyinNormal.en: Is this an actual emergency? Yes! Even if it's not, Momma loves a practice drill.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是真的紧急情况吗？是的。即便不是，妈妈也喜欢实战演习。

yingyinNormal.en: Daddy Pig, you are not supposed to ring on this phone. It's only for emergencies. This is an emergency. I can't find the tomato ketchup anywhere.
yingyinNormal.zh: 猪爸爸，你不应该打这个电话的。这是紧急情况时才使用的。可我就是有紧急情况啊。我到处找不到番茄酱，怎么办啊。

yingyinNormal.en: In case of emergency, please contact, Amy Farrah Fowler. And there's my phone number.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一旦发生紧急情况，请与艾米·菲拉·福勒联系，还有我的电话号码。

yingyinNormal.en: Matthews family emergency! Move, move, move, move! Everybody out of the house in under 10 seconds! Yes!
yingyinNormal.zh: 马修斯家紧急情况！快跑！快跑！所有人在十秒钟内跑出了屋子，赞！

yingyinNormal.en: Supe? Yeah? I have an emergency. What's the report? Both engines. What? Both engines gone. No thrust.
yingyinNormal.zh: 主管？嗯？我这有紧急情况。什么状况？双发停车。什么？双发都停车了，没有推力。

yingyinNormal.en: I will argue that the emergency met the legal doctrine of quod est necessarium est licitum that which is necessary is legal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要争辩的是紧急情况下的法律原理是需要即合法[拉丁文]，也就是需要即合法。

yingyinNormal.en: 911, what's your emergency? Hi, I'm calling about a possible... I'm calling to report a missing person. Okay, who is this regarding? My daughter.
yingyinNormal.zh: 圣何塞失踪人口这里是911，你的紧急情况是？嗨，我这边有可能...我... 我要报告一起失踪事件。好的，谁失踪了？圣何塞失踪人口报告 国家失踪及不明身份人员系统 我女儿。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, I like their emergency room.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我好喜欢他们的急诊室。

yingyinNormal.en: Monica, what? What? What is the emergency?
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么紧急大事？

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, now, after the emergency trip to that salon.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在才不错，多亏了我跑去发廊紧急补救。

yingyinNormal.en: Dr. Ramoray, report to first floor Emergency stat.
yingyinNormal.zh: 雷莫瑞大夫，请到一楼急诊室。

yingyinNormal.en: Belt! Emergency Idea Generator, activate! I've got it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 皮带猴! 紧急想法发生器，启动! 我想到了。

yingyinNormal.en: You're in my bedroom. Leonard gave me an emergency key.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你在我的卧室里。莱纳德给了我应急钥匙。

yingyinNormal.en: An emergency injunction against the museum to stop the exhibition.
yingyinNormal.zh: 申请对博物馆的紧急禁令使其停止展览。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

examination_example.sentence: There are also <highlight>Emergency</highlight> Tree Care Volunteers at the FUF.
It aims to improve their abilities (能力) to deal with a first aid <highlight>emergency</highlight> (紧急情况).
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它旨在提高他们处理急救紧急情况的能力。

examination_example.sentence: As long as he describes the buildings around, the dispatcher can dispatch <highlight>emergency</highlight> medical workers to him.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 只要他描述一下周围的建筑，调度员就可以向他派出紧急医疗人员。

examination_example.sentence: They remember every corner of the city through hand-made maps, and dispatch <highlight>emergency</highlight> medical workers to the right place as soon as possible.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们通过手工制作的地图记住城市的每一个角落，并尽快派遣紧急医疗人员到正确的地方。

examination_example.sentence: We must get clear information about the patient in 60 seconds and dispatch(调度) <highlight>emergency</highlight> medical workers in 3 minutes at most.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们必须在60秒内获得患者的明确信息，最多在3分钟内派遣急救人员。
